{
  "page": "Walder of Woodmere",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The canonicity of the character presented in this article is currently unclear. They are not mentioned in the written works of <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>. However, they are mentioned in the <a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">graphic novel adaptation</a> of <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i>, in the <a href=\"/index.php/List_of_characters_and_arms_in_The_Hedge_Knight_graphic_novel_collection\" title=\"List of characters and arms in The Hedge Knight graphic novel collection\">roll of arms</a> of the attendees of the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Ashford_Meadow\" title=\"Tourney at Ashford Meadow\">tourney at Ashford Meadow</a>. Until further information comes out, they should be considered a semi-canon character.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Rivers\" title=\"Walder Rivers\"><img alt=\"Walder Rivers.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/82/Walder_Rivers.svg/50px-Walder_Rivers.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/82/Walder_Rivers.svg/75px-Walder_Rivers.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/82/Walder_Rivers.svg/100px-Walder_Rivers.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Walder of Woodmere</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Rivers\" title=\"Walder Rivers\"><img alt=\"Walder Rivers.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/82/Walder_Rivers.svg/50px-Walder_Rivers.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/82/Walder_Rivers.svg/75px-Walder_Rivers.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/82/Walder_Rivers.svg/100px-Walder_Rivers.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Personal arms</span></th><td>\nA silver-grey castle on blue beneath a red bend sinister<br />(<i>Azure, beneath a bend sinister gules a bridge cendrée, at either end a tower of the same</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">Graphic Novel</a> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Ser <b>Walder of Woodmere</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Woodmere\" title=\"Woodmere\">Woodmere</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walder_of_Woodmere&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Walder was listed as a participant of the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Ashford_Meadow\" title=\"Tourney at Ashford Meadow\">tourney at Ashford Meadow</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Arms\">Arms</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walder_of_Woodmere&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Arms\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The roll of arms in the first edition of the <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i> <a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">graphic novel</a> displayed Walder's sigil as a blue plate on white, similar to the arms of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Poole\" title=\"House Poole\">House Poole</a>. However, in later editions, his sigil was changed to a grey castle on blue beneath a red bend sinister<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> (same as the arms of <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Rivers\" title=\"Walder Rivers\">Walder Rivers</a>), suggesting that Walder of Woodmere was a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walder_of_Woodmere&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rthk_.5B.5Bthe_hedge_knight_.28comics.29.7Cgraphic_novel.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i>,  <a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">Graphic Novel</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/List_of_characters_and_arms_in_The_Hedge_Knight_graphic_novel_collection\" title=\"List of characters and arms in The Hedge Knight graphic novel collection\">List of characters and arms in The Hedge Knight graphic novel collection‎</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404084704\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.092 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.335 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 523/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10784/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9446/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2081/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1413/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.230/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  323.318      1 -total\n 96.08%  310.630      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.71%  309.460      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.43%   36.967     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.89%   19.034      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.32%    4.271      2 Template:Ref\n  1.18%    3.830      1 Template:Date\n  0.72%    2.343      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.65%    2.095      1 Template:Notice/THK_roll\n  0.57%    1.842      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:21591-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404084703 and revision id 326684\n -->\n",
